des:
Some Music presents the finest in 1-minute music clips. 
Listen to rock, contemporary, classical, ambient, world, national, and more!

Just open the skill by saying to your echo, “Alexa, open Some Music.”
You can say yes to automatically link to Song Quiz, or keep listening to music for as long as you want.
It’s that easy!

If you enjoyed this skill, please leave us a review! Thanks!
